[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "みんな、いらっしゃい！\n第１回九偉人会を始めるわよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00955",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "リーベ",
		"romanized_name": "Liebe",
		"model_path_hash": "281475164831455342",
		"text": "ヴァレリア、説明を求めます。九偉人会とやらの\n目的と、そこのヘルト兄様とゼロ姉様について",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_156_037_00956",
		"still_path_hash": "5075029600051949533",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "私もよく分からないんだけどヘルトに元気がないの。\nだから美味しいものを食べて元気出してもらおうって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00957",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "兄者を元気づけようとする、その気持ちやよし！\n我の力は兄者の賢い知恵があってこそ輝くからのお！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_00958",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "それに私、果ての大陸へ向けて\n一度兄弟全員で集まってみたいと思っていたのよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00959",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "あの、ヘルト兄貴もゼロ姉貴も、来て大丈夫なの？\n王都で囚われてるはずじゃ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_00960",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "そこはクレオたちが手を回してくれたのよ。\n一家団らんは大切だから、特別にって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00961",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ゴゥ",
		"romanized_name": "Gou",
		"model_path_hash": "5559160385657202980",
		"text": "一家団らん……！\nいいぞ、兄弟みんな仲良く……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_155_037_00962",
		"still_path_hash": "2242265198409136417",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "それで、美味しいものを食べるってことだけど、\nもう用意してあるのかい？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_00963",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ええ！　ランツェに手伝ってもらって、\n私が用意したわ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00964",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "ヴァレリア姉上の料理……\n肉、丸焼き……魚、丸焼き……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_037_00965",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "我は空腹じゃ！　はよ食事の席に案内せえ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_00966",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "はーい。みんなあっちよ、ついてきて。\nほら、ヘルトも",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00967",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_00968",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "なんだい、シトリン。\nあんな様子でも、ヘル兄が怖いかい？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_00969",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "……いや、さすがにそこまでビビりじゃないけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_00970",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "ただ、調子が狂うなって。それだけ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_00971",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]